data.title: Caltech vs MIT: How Do They Compare [2024]
data.meta_description: The California Institute of Technology, more popularly known as Caltech, is a private research university world-renowned for its contributions to science, engineering, and technology. Massachusetts Institute of Technology, or MIT, is a private research university now located in Cambridge, Massachusetts.
